    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary 3.2L S54 inline-six powerplant. This high-revving engine delivers exceptional linear power through individual throttle bodies and is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis is well-maintained, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. Recent technical updates include a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal timing and compression. While the finish shows signs of honest road use, the suspension remains taut with communicative hydraulic steering, making this an ideal candidate for the purist seeking a visceral driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
