      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, with the paint showing very well and only minor stone chips consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment where the upholstery remains firm and free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is ready for the road. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and within the last six months, it has received new brake pads and a fresh battery. The engine runs quietly, the steering is tight, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a reliable, attractive, and well-documented example that is ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
