    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a definitive mid-engine driver\u2019s car. Powered by the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six boxer engine, this unit remains free of IMS weeping and exhibits no signs of bore scoring. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a clutch that retains excellent take-up feel. Performance is enhanced by the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system, providing active damping control, and 4-piston monoblock fixed calipers for consistent deceleration. Recent service includes a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump and a fresh serpentine belt. The chassis remains taut, riding on staggered alloys wrapped in high-performance rubber. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the hydraulic steering rack and Variocam Plus timing\u2014are in peak operating condition.",
